At the table in Gedda they will not sit either Trump, it is Zelensky. The leader of Kiev will be in Saudi Arabia for an interview - previously scheduled - with Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman at Riad. For Ukraine, Gedda will be the head of the presidential office Andriy Yermak, the national security advisor and foreign and defence ministers. For the United States, the Secretary of State Marco Rubio> and National Security Councillor Mike Waltz will participate. The American envoy for the Middle East Steve Witkoff hoped that the Gedda negotiations will put things back on track.
